preownedConditionTypes.conditionTypeDefinition: Item is in excellent condition, perfect working condition and has no signs of wear/usage. The original protective wrapping, if any, may be missing but the original packaging is intact.

Item is in excellent condition and has no signs of usage. The item is still in its original packaging, but packaging is open/has signs of wear. The item includes original accessories. This could include warehouse items, returns, etc.
Item shows wear from consistent use, but it remains in fair condition. The item may be marked, identified, or show other signs of previous use. The item remains usable.
A well-cared-for item that has seen limited use but remains in great condition. Item and instructions are complete and included.
A brand-new, unused functional item that has cosmetic imperfections caused during production or delivery. (Missing threads, discoloration, label malfunction, etc.)
A brand-new, unused item without original packaging.
A brand-new, unused item without original tags.
An original name brand cartridge that has been professionally cleaned, refilled with similar quality ink, and then tested to make sure you get the same print quality as the original cartridge.

_rawConfigs.promotionTitle: Save up to 35% on additional pairs
_rawConfigs.termsText:
Purchase multiple pairs of eyeglasses (frame & prescription lenses) to get 20% off each additional pair of glasses after your first order. Multiple qualifying glasses must be purchased during a single online transaction. Qualifying purchases include: a complete pair of prescription eyeglasses (frame & prescription lenses) or an insurance order for a complete pair of glasses. Insurance benefits should be maximized on the first order (if applicable).

Discounts must be applied to qualifying orders that are of equal or lesser value. For 35% off, purchase a complete pair of sunglasses in addition to a second complete pair. Qualifying purchases include any prescription polarized or non-polarized sun lens & frame purchase. The least expensive pair(s) will receive the 35% discount.

addOnServices.serviceSubTitle: Get peace of mind for pennies a day!

groups.shortDescription:
Protect it today, enjoy it for years.

Extend and enhance your manufacturer's warranty with a Walmart Protection Plan.

Plans for TVs cover:

  • Screen, remote, and speaker failure
  • Power surges and power supply failure
  • 24/7 customer support for fast repairs and replacements
  • 100% parts and labor covered, no hidden fees

Never lose your plan details again.

Simply add a Walmart Protection Plan to your order and check out as usual. There is no need to register your plan for it to be active. Your plan details will be sent to your email address as well as stored in your Walmart.com account.

addOnServices.serviceSubTitle: Our professionals do it right & fast

groups.shortDescription:
For less than the price of a weekly coffee, you can receive one year of Premium Tech Support & Security powered by True Network Solutions. Our US-based tech experts are available 24/7 by phone, chat, or email to assist you when you need it!


For only $99, this $400 value includes unlimited support for all the tech you own — computers, smart home products, printers, routers, tablets, and more.


What's included with this 1-year service?

  • McAfee Total Protection to defend against viruses & online threats
  • Unlimited 24/7 1-on-1 tech coaching and tech support with live multi-lingual US-based Tech Experts
  • Unlimited virus removal for up to 10 devices
  • Initial Setup service and ongoing support for any of your tech products, no matter where you bought them
  • Access to 1 Data Recovery service: if your computer suffers a data loss, we can recover it free of charge*
  • Unlimited troubleshooting, software support, and PC tune-ups


Questions? Call (316) 776-4357 to learn more from our friendly tech team.



How do I receive service?

Simply add this service to your cart and check out. Once purchased, you'll receive an email from True Network with the information needed to initiate service at your convenience. You'll be able to call, email, or chat 24/7/365 with a US-based tech expert


How long do I receive service for?

This is a one-year service plan and does not auto-renew.


True Satisfaction

True Network Solutions is committed to making sure every customer is happy with our services! We'll do everything possible to make sure our customers are 100% satisfied. If you would like to provide feedback on your experience or encounter any issues, we're ready to listen. Contact our Customer Service team 24/7 at (316) 776-4357.


* We use commercially reasonable efforts to attempt to recover your lost data and files using both basic and advanced methods. Methods include but are not limited to current software and hardware techniques available as well as proprietary techniques developed for data recovery.

idml.longDescription:
• Intel Core Ultra - Unlock AI Experiences. Whether you're working, collaborating, creating or playing, Intel® Core™ Ultra 7processor155H processor delivers a dedicated engine to help unlock AI experiences on the PC, the next level in immersive graphics, and high-performance low power processing, so you can confidently perform for longer while unplugged.
  • AI-Powered Graphics - Experience fast-paced gaming with GeForce RTX™ 4070 laptop graphics. Dive deep intolifelike visuals and unparalleled performance, all amplified by NVIDIA DLSS 3 technology. Harness AI-driven advancements for smoother, more immersive gameplaythat keeps you at the edge of your seat.
  • Clarity, Competitive Edge - Plunge into a vast 14.5-inch display, illuminated with brilliant colors, and framed in a16:10 aspect ratio. The pristine WQXGA boasts a fast 120Hz refresh rate, and with 100% sRGB color gamut, you're assured lifelike hues. Enhanced by NVIDIA® G-SYNC® and NVIDIA Advanced Optimus, enjoy seamless tear-free gaming.
  • Start Your Engines - This Predator Helios Neo 14 laptop will take your game library, place it in front of you, anddare you to give it a challenge. Not only does Helios look good while dishing out frame after frame, but this RTX-empowered machine is fully optimized for maximum 110W MGP usage, so you always have two things: Full Power.
  • NVIDIA® Advanced Optimus® - NVIDIA® Advanced Optimus allows the display to dynamically switch between theintegrated graphics and the discrete graphics without having to reboot. The result increased game performance, reduced system latency when gaming, and it enables the use of G-SYNC variable refresh rate displays, improving users’ experiences.
  • Peak Performance Guaranteed - Keep cool under pressure. With the 5th Gen AeroBlade™ 3D Fan Technology, vectorheat pipes, and liquid metal thermal grease, you can maintain top performance ineven the most heated moments. The dual-fan system with VortexFlow improvescooling efficiency by consistently drawing in colder air into the system's interior.

customerReviews.reviewText: [This review was collected as part of a promotion.] The new Predator 14' laptop is fast and fun to play. It was easy to set up the pre-installed Windows 11. The graphics are great and definitely an upgrade from older i7. The speed is also quite impressive. It's not as heavy as most gaming laptops. However, the charger is still heavy.

[This review was collected as part of a promotion.] Really easy setup and installs of the the necessary systems. Loving the display and portability of the laptop, I wish the fan was a little quieter, however I'm able to push the computer to get over 144FPS while playing games. I've been leaving it plugged in in order to conserve battery but extremely happy with the performance so far.
customerReviews.reviewTitle: Portable gaming without a loss of quality

customerReviews.reviewText: [This review was collected as part of a promotion.] The build quality is top notch with a beautiful 14 inch display. This light yet versatile gaming laptop is ultra portable with great performance for its size. One thing that could be better is the battery life though. All in all a great little gaming laptop!
customerReviews.reviewTitle: It's ultra light weight and super fast but make sure you have your charger handy!

customerReviews.reviewText: [This review was collected as part of a promotion.] Wow!!! This small gaming laptop packs a punch. The packaging was very neat, organized, and secure. Battery life is very good even when it runs on performance mode. The graphics card in this laptop is superb for the price point and just as good as an expensive monitor. Playing online gaming through wifi is practically effortless, and there is no lag. The led keyboard has a nice look to it. The keys feel sturdy and are easy to use.

[This review was collected as part of a promotion.] This laptop has great performance for almost any task. I used it for gaming and photo editing. The display is crisp and action games feel smooth. It's not too heavy and would be easily transportable. However, the battery life wasn't amazing, but it was decent for a computer this size. I got about 3.5 hours while playing video games. Overall, a great choice for performance and display quality.

[This review was collected as part of a promotion.] RTX 4060 and meteor lake cpu can run any of the latest games like elden ring on max settings. The laptop is 5G compatible, allowing fast connection for low latency games like counter strike and league. rainbow keyboard backlight. May need some cooling when running more demanding applications for extended time. The screen is on the smaller side, but the laptop is compact and fits easily in a small compartment. Highly recommend to gamers looking for a good deal on a gaming laptop.

[This review was collected as part of a promotion.] I love this laptop it's perfect for gaming especially on the go and the quality of the display is great. The battery last a long time which is usually rare when using gaming applications. Highly recommend!

[This review was collected as part of a promotion.] Best for all kinds of works including video and photos editing. I love playing with my fantastic entry level gaming PC. I love the keyboard it lights up different colors while you use it. The battery life lasts a long time.
computer performs very well and look very clean

[This review was collected as part of a promotion.] The gaming laptop takes a while to start up. I was so impressed by the RGB four-color on keyboard and logo Predator. It helps me see clearly while playing or working in the dark. The touchpad is larger than other laptops and very sensitive. Gaming laptop has good quality speaker. Also, it has PredatorSense software, which makes it easy to adjust preferences. The Gaming Laptop runs smoothly while playing games.
